Spearker's bio: Mark Richard, Product Manager for Oxford University Press, is an experienced presenter with fifteen years of teaching and training in France, Taiwan, Japan, Korea, Vietnam and, Indonesia. He has taught practically every age groups, in a variety of instructions. Mark is particularly interested in how students' brains work to process and remember what they are taught.

