自學園 敬啟[2012.04.20] 線上作文諮詢的檔案格式Dear students, 

When uploading your writing, please make sure that it is in .doc file format rather than in.docx format. Although word document can be in either .doc or .docx format, the former can be directly opened in word 2003 and higher. Thanks for your help. 

各位同學好： 

當使用Office 2007或Office2010時，請將檔案存成word97-2003格式 (*.doc)而非word 格式(*.docx)。之後再上傳檔案。謝謝：) 

